{"content": "<p>You are eligible for a free mint +gas ⛽️ for the <a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0xe125091e7c669d47e374d7f23bc857789f701780/2\">10k Project</a> if you were <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1523470586617675776?s=20&amp;t=3LmWCy8rwpHfx1KXajicOw\">following MintFace</a> on Twitter before Saturday 7th May 2022.</p><p>If you filled in the Google Form on Sunday, check your wallet. You will see the 10k Project NFT is already there. 🥰👀</p><p>If you are yet to claim yours, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1523470586617675776?s=20&amp;t=3LmWCy8rwpHfx1KXajicOw\">let MintFace know on Twitter</a> which mint face you are in the 10k Project.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">🍒Which mint face are you in the 10k Project?<br /><br />Row # <br />Column # <br />Wallet address:<br /><br />🎁Receive a free +gas ⛽️ private sale setup for...<a href=\"https://t.co/dJfHE5Sp8m\">https://t.co/dJfHE5Sp8m</a><br /><br />🍒if you added your details already yesterday, no need to enter, check your wallet 👀 <a href=\"https://t.co/4iivlonduq\">pic.twitter.com/4iivlonduq</a></p>&mdash; MintFace.eth 🍒 (@mintfaced) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/mintfaced/status/1523470586617675776?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 9, 2022</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></figure><h3 id=\"wen-mint\">wen mint</h3><p>You can <a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0xe125091e7c669d47e374d7f23bc857789f701780/2\">pick up a 10k edition</a> showing the surreal beauty of our collective pfps even if you don't follow MintFace. For the art. For the culture. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card kg-nft-card\">            <a class=\"kg-nft-card-container\" href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0xe125091e7c669d47e374d7f23bc857789f701780/2\" data-payload=\"%7B%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fopensea.io%2Fassets%2F0xe125091e7c669d47e374d7f23bc857789f701780%2F2%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22nft%22%2C%22metadata%22%3A%7B%22version%22%3A%221.0%22%2C%22title%22%3A%2210k%20Project%22%2C%22author_name%22%3A%22mintface%22%2C%22author_url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fopensea.io%2Fmintface%22%2C%22provider_name%22%3A%22OpenSea%22%2C%22provider_url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fopensea.io%22%2C%22image_url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fw7P5lfibnBE3h8a8OPdeVyT4SR9i-JFeBSstR2iKRdMOGXyZ92ymGpgRr2ngVzMvHuXpq_QJeTK4di5k0y08OL3aboDJlIrkWZa1VZA%22%2C%22creator_name%22%3A%22mintface%22%2C%22description%22%3A%22The%2010k%20Project%20is%20a%20love%20letter%20to%20the%20first%2010%2C000%20mint%20faces%20who%20joined%20in%20the%20NFT%20fun%20in%202021%2F2022%20by%20following%20%40MintFaced%20on%20Twitter.%5Cn%5CnThank%20you%20for%20joining%20NFTs%20and%20making%20the%20community%20what%20it%20has%20become.%5Cn%5CnKeep%20creating.%22%2C%22collection_name%22%3A%2210K%20Project%22%7D%7D\">                <div class=\"kg-ntf-image-container\"><img class=\"kg-nft-image\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/w7P5lfibnBE3h8a8OPdeVyT4SR9i-JFeBSstR2iKRdMOGXyZ92ymGpgRr2ngVzMvHuXpq_QJeTK4di5k0y08OL3aboDJlIrkWZa1VZA\"></div>                <div class=\"kg-nft-metadata\">                    <div class=\"kg-nft-header\">                        <h4 class=\"kg-nft-title\"> 10k Project </h4>                        <img src=\"https://static.ghost.org/v4.0.0/images/opensea-logo.png\" class=\"kg-nft-opensea-logo\">                    </div>                    <div class=\"kg-nft-creator\">                        Created by <span class=\"kg-nft-creator-name\">mintface</span>                        &bull; 10K Project                    </div>                    <p class=\"kg-nft-description\">The 10k Project is a love letter to the first 10,000 mint faces who joined in the NFT fun in 2021/2022 by following @MintFaced on Twitter.Thank you for joining NFTs and making the community what it has become.Keep creating.</p>                </div>            </a>        </figure><h3 id=\"wen-utility\">wen utility</h3><p>Add your 10K Project artwork to an OnCyber loft like loopmaniac.eth has done.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/05/FSSE9MrUcAAwNnT.jpeg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1235\" height=\"1344\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/FSSE9MrUcAAwNnT.jpeg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/FSSE9MrUcAAwNnT.jpeg 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/05/FSSE9MrUcAAwNnT.jpeg 1235w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>The second utility yet to be enabled is using your own mint face edition as a pass to go places in MintFace spaces in om such as MintFacePlace.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/05/mintfaceplace.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1464\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w600/2022/05/mintfaceplace.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1000/2022/05/mintfaceplace.png 1000w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/size/w1600/2022/05/mintfaceplace.png 1600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/2022/05/mintfaceplace.png 2000w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><p>Some MintPasses are <a href=\"https://opensea.io/assets/0xe35cb2bea009c4b40643d4970388ebf47446c899/15\">more special</a> than others.</p><hr />"}